OL,7,FResidents in Aberfan fear losing the
OL,8,Fcommunity centre which "helped them
OL,9,Frecover" from the 1966 disaster which
OL,10,Fclaimed the lives of 144 people.
OL,12,FMany fear they could lose access to
OL,13,Fthe community hub in Merthyr Tydfil
OL,14,Fwhich was their "beacon of hope" if a
OL,15,Flegal dispute is not resolved.
