OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,FAberfan and Merthyr Vale Community
OL,8,FCentre, which opened in 1973, was paid
OL,9,Ffor with money donated to the 1966
OL,10,FDisaster Fund and is now the beating
OL,11,Fheart of the village, with King
OL,12,FCharles visiting to mark the 50th
OL,13,Fanniversary of the disaster in 2016 to
OL,14,Fdeliver a heartfelt message from the
OL,15,Flate Queen.
OL,17,FBut contract complexities threaten its
OL,18,Ffuture.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
