OL,4,Ccommunity hub that 'helped them
OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,FThe centre is currently operated by
OL,8,FWellbeing Merthyr, formerly known as
OL,9,FMerthyr Leisure Trust, but their
OL,10,Fcontract to run the facility is coming
OL,11,Fto an end on March 31, and work is
OL,12,Fongoing to try and approve a handover
OL,13,Fof the centre back to Merthyr Tydfil
OL,14,Fcouncil, who want to appoint an
OL,15,Falternative provider to run the centre.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
