OL,3,CAberfan residents worried about losing
OL,4,Ccommunity hub that 'helped them
OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,FGareth Morgans, from GMB union, said
OL,8,Fof worried staff who work at the
OL,9,Fcentre: "They're angry. They've got an
OL,10,Funcertain future. They don't know if
OL,11,Fthis place will be open from the 1
OL,12,FApril. Obviously they're concerned
OL,13,Fabout their future.
OL,15,F"We are trying to bang some heads
OL,16,Ftogether. The council don't seem to be
OL,17,Ftalking to the leisure trust, and vice
OL,18,Fversa. We are trying to get them to
OL,19,Ftalk to each other to try and get the
OL,20,Fstewardship and guardianship back into
OL,21,Fthe local authority."
