OL,4,Ccommunity hub that 'helped them
OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,FDenise Morgan, who lost her sister in
OL,8,Fthe 1966 coal tip disaster, said the
OL,9,F"Aberfan building was a beacon of
OL,10,Fhope" in the village's recovery.
OL,12,FShe said: "That building helped us to
OL,13,Frecover. And it was obviously a beacon
OL,14,Fof hope at the time that we could go
OL,15,Fsomewhere and forget in part about
OL,16,Fwhat had happened and make more
OL,17,Fmemories with the generations that
OL,18,Fwere growing up in Aberfan then."
