OL,3,CAberfan residents worried about losing
OL,4,Ccommunity hub that 'helped them
OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,FNow, the centre welcomes visitors of
OL,8,Fall ages, and has been the home of the
OL,9,Fonly public swimming pool in Merthyr
OL,10,Ffor a number of years.
OL,12,FNew mum Jodie Williams and baby Mila
OL,13,Fattend Aqua-tots classes every week at
OL,14,Fthe centre, and want to see the
OL,15,Fcentre's future resolved.
OL,17,FJodie said: "Being on maternity, it is
OL,18,Fquite lonely. So I do like to go to
OL,19,Fthese classes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
