OL,3,CAberfan residents worried about losing
OL,4,Ccommunity hub that 'helped them
OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,F"I'm a PE teacher, so going swimming
OL,8,Ffor me is like a breath of fresh air,
OL,9,Fand taking my daughter thinking 'okay,
OL,10,FI know she's not going to be swimming
OL,11,Flengths', but it's just that
OL,12,Fconfidence that she's gaining in the
OL,13,Fwater."
OL,15,FThe local authority said they
OL,16,F"appreciate the historical
OL,17,Fsignificance" of the building ut this
OL,18,Fis a complex legal issue.
