OL,4,Ccommunity hub that 'helped them
OL,5,Crecover'
OL,7,FEllis Cooper, chief executive of
OL,8,FMerthyr Tydfil council, said: "The
OL,9,Fcouncil has been very clear in its
OL,10,Fintention of what it wants to do. We
OL,11,Fwant to maintain services for the
OL,12,Fpeople of Aberfan.
OL,14,F"We want the trust to meet us half
OL,15,Fway, and work with us and find that
OL,16,Fresolution for the people of Merthyr
OL,17,FTydfil, and for Aberfan in particular."
