OL,7,FWellbeing Merthyr told ITV Wales they
OL,8,Fwant to alleviate concerns of the
OL,9,Fcommunity and they want a managed
OL,10,Freturn of the services in this
OL,11,Fbuilding to the local authority, and
OL,12,Fthey will be working with the council
OL,13,Fto achieve that.
